# The bot image is a single-project publish of Source/ (plus the root build config).
# Keep the build context small and deterministic: exclude build output, VCS, tooling,
# and everything the app image does not need. Do NOT exclude the root MSBuild config
# (Directory.Build.props, Directory.Packages.props, global.json, .globalconfig,
# .editorconfig) — the publish needs them.

# Build output
**/bin/
**/obj/

# VCS and tooling
.git/
.gitattributes
.github/
.claude/
.vs/
.vscode/
*.user

# Content the bot image does not need (Source/ is the only project it publishes)
Specs/
Eval/
Planning/
Documentation/
docker-compose.yml
